Hi there!

You can read some of my other posts at any or all of the links below:

Blog: mrdaps.com
Website: dapsmagic.com
Twitter: twitter.com/mrdaps
Facebook: facebook.com/misterdaps

Please feel free to add me on any or all of the above links. I look forward to chatting with you and seeing you in the park!

Make it a GREAT day!

-Mr. DAPs

title: Avengers Endgame emotions and songs
body:
Here’s a list of songs to help:

  • Ashes to ashes- David Bowie (I know this one is cruel)
  • The Avengers- Earth’s Mightiest Heroes
  • Brothers under the sun (for Loki)- Bryan Adams
  • Captain America The Winter Soldier The Smithsonian

  • I love you always forever- Donna Lewis
  • I ship it- Not Literally

  • Running Scared- Ell, Nikki
